{"tid":2115994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：如疫情再惡化應實施居家令 政府應擺街站派樽","createTime":"2020-07-20T01:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T21:51:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":191,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"3b1ae043436c508d640c11200a6647e79db5cee7","tid":2115994,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:19:50.000Z","msg":"港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇在本台節目指，相比起本港2月及3月的疫情，港人現時失去了抗疫恐慌心理，開始增加社交活動以及少了戴口罩，確診個案上升是當然，形容第三波疫情的爆發是因為輕敵，認為市民都知要如何防疫，呼籲切實執行戴口罩，在疫苗面世前都不要鬆懈。 <br />\n<br />\n袁國勇認為政府再收緊防疫措施是做得對，要做好邊境管理及防止內部擴散的風險，如果7至14日後確診個案數字仍呈幾何級數上升，應該實施居家令。對於慈雲山出現大批確診病例，袁國勇建議當局在當區擺街站派發深喉唾液樣本瓶，供有需要居民取用，全港街市亦應提供消毒搓手液。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2347983\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2347983&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=545be6ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2347983</a>"},{"pid":"8c04961355093e912401d99510a2b82b48b3ed62","tid":2115994,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ba941314d640a63109a93c82732cfed7a63f98","tid":2115994,"uid":76341,"like":17,"dislike":69,"score":-52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:20:31.000Z","msg":"又響度亂講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9edcac97439496117a5badf243f41ebfa964dbc","tid":2115994,"uid":88743,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:21:27.000Z","msg":"今日去超市搶咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704c0eae30c9702aeb83bb3df3dcad8355284ac9","tid":2115994,"uid":35330,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T01:21:30.000Z","msg":"居家令去到政苦到咪即係宵禁<br />\n日頭最緊要返工<img